DefaultReaderConfiguration.preQueryCheck: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM events_rpt_v3 WHERE date_created > ?
DefaultReaderConfiguration.queryString: SELECT e.date_created AS ResultScanDate, e.event_datetime, e.rv40, e.base_message, e.init_ip_dotted, e.init_host_name, e.init_host_domain, e.init_user_name, e.init_user_domain, e.init_service_port_name, e.target_ip_dotted, e.target_host_name, e.target_host_domain, e.target_service_port_name, e.target_user_name, e.target_user_domain, e.init_service_comp, e.file_name, e.cv52 FROM events_rpt_v3 e WHERE e.date_created > ? ORDER BY e.date_created;
